@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@token =

### 审计记录导出取证（分页拉取）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 登录日志取证
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login-logs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 当前鉴权身份校验取证
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 安全健康探测取证
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/secure/ping
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 系统监控取证
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/monitor/server-info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
